<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto p-3 md:p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 via-white to-pink-50 rounded-3xl shadow-xl" data-controller="exercise-checker">

  <!-- Header -->
  <div class="mb-8">
    <div class="flex items-start sm:items-center justify-between gap-4 mb-4">
      <div class="flex flex-col-reverse sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center gap-2 sm:gap-4">
        <div class="bg-purple-600 text-white text-md sm:text-xl px-2 sm:px-4 py-1.5 sm:py-2 rounded-lg font-bold">
          VERIFICA
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-purple-600">Le parti invariabili del discorso</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="flex-shrink-0 bg-red-600 text-white rounded-full w-10 h-10 sm:w-12 sm:h-12 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg sm:text-xl">
        95
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 4 -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border-4 border-blue-200 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-blue-700 mb-4">
      <span class="bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center mr-2">4</span>
      Riscrivi le frasi sul quaderno sostituendo le congiunzioni con altre congiunzioni in modo che le frasi abbiano comunque senso. Osserva l'esempio.
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg">
      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <div class="mb-2">
          <span class="text-gray-700">• Elsa si è slogata una caviglia, <strong>quindi</strong> l'abbiamo portata dal dottore.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="text-sm text-gray-600 pl-4">
          → <em>Elsa si è slogata una caviglia, <strong>perciò</strong> l'abbiamo portata dal dottore.</em>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• <strong>Poiché</strong> sei arrivata prima, meriti un premio.</span>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• Umberto suona la chitarra <strong>e</strong> Rossella canta.</span>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• Il posto è libero, <strong>perciò</strong> puoi sederti.</span>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• Porto il pane, <strong>però</strong> non è fresco.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 5 -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border-4 border-green-200 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6" data-controller="fill-blanks">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-green-700 mb-4">
      <span class="bg-green-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center mr-2">5</span>
      Completa con le congiunzioni adatte.
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg">
      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-gray-700">• Chiudo la porta</span>
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-green-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 w-32" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="perché" data-correct-answer="perché" placeholder="..........">
          <span class="text-gray-700">fa freddo.</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-gray-700">• Siamo molto amici</span>
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-green-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 w-32" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="ma" data-correct-answer="ma" placeholder="..........">
          <span class="text-gray-700">non ci vediamo quasi mai</span>
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-green-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 w-32" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="perché" data-correct-answer="perché" placeholder="..........">
          <span class="text-gray-700">abitiamo lontano.</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-gray-700">• L'acqua è preziosa</span>
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-green-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 w-32" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="perciò" data-correct-answer="perciò" placeholder="..........">
          <span class="text-gray-700">cerchiamo di non sprecarla.</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-gray-700">• Non so</span>
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-green-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 w-32" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="se" data-correct-answer="se" placeholder="..........">
          <span class="text-gray-700">uscirò</span>
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-green-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 w-32" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="o" data-correct-answer="o" placeholder="..........">
          <span class="text-gray-700">rimarrò in casa.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 6 -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border-4 border-purple-200 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-purple-700 mb-4">
      <span class="bg-purple-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center mr-2">6</span>
      Sottolinea le congiunzioni coordinative e cerchia le congiunzioni subordinative.
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-2 text-base md:text-lg">
      <div class="bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• La squadra ha giocato bene <strong class="underline">ma</strong> ha perso.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• Hai saputo <strong class="border-2 border-purple-500 rounded px-1">che</strong> Giuditta cambia scuola?</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• Sono fratelli <strong class="border-2 border-purple-500 rounded px-1">benché</strong> non si assomiglino.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• Andiamo a piedi <strong class="underline">o</strong> prendiamo le bici?</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Le mie competenze section -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-100 to-amber-100 rounded-2xl border-4 border-yellow-300 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-yellow-700 mb-6 text-center">
      Le mie competenze
    </h2>

    <!-- Exercise 7 -->
    <div data-controller="multiple-choice">
      <h3 class="text-base md:text-lg font-bold text-gray-700 mb-3">
        <span class="bg-yellow-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 inline-flex items-center justify-center mr-2">7</span>
        Leggi la seguente frase.
      </h3>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-4 border-2 border-yellow-200 mb-4">
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 font-semibold italic text-center">
          "Halyna va di rado in montagna, sebbene cammini volentieri."
        </p>
      </div>

      <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 font-semibold mb-3">Qual è l'unica affermazione vera?</p>

      <div class="space-y-2 text-base md:text-lg">
        <label class="flex items-start gap-2 bg-white border-2 border-yellow-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-yellow-50">
          <input type="checkbox" name="ex7" value="A" class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5">
          <span class="text-gray-700">Nella frase ci sono soltanto una congiunzione e un avverbio.</span>
        </label>

        <label class="flex items-start gap-2 bg-white border-2 border-yellow-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-yellow-50">
          <input type="checkbox" name="ex7" value="B" class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5">
          <span class="text-gray-700">Nella frase ci sono soltanto una locuzione avverbiale e una congiunzione.</span>
        </label>

        <label class="flex items-start gap-2 bg-white border-2 border-yellow-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-yellow-50">
          <input type="checkbox" name="ex7" value="C" class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5">
          <span class="text-gray-700">Nella frase ci sono due avverbi e una congiunzione.</span>
        </label>

        <label class="flex items-start gap-2 bg-white border-2 border-yellow-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-yellow-50">
          <input type="checkbox" name="ex7" value="D" class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5">
          <span class="text-gray-700">Nella frase ci sono una locuzione avverbiale, un avverbio e una congiunzione.</span>
        </label>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%= render partial: "shared/exercise_controls" %>

</div>
